data.description: Dreaming of a deluxe on-suite bath with a spa-like shower? You’ll love this stunning home that features a shower with a rainfall shower head and two additional shower heads, giving you the ultimate relaxation experience. But that’s not all. This home also boasts a cozy gas fireplace, a 3 season room where you can enjoy the fresh air, and amazing landscaping that will make your neighbors jealous. And did we mention the spacious 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 2 stall garage on the alley? This home has it all and more. Don’t miss this opportunity to own your dream home. Schedule a showing today!
